  "description": [
    "Triumph of Socialist Agriculture By R SERGEEV Editor of Machine Tractor Stations The Soviet village meets the fourteenth anniversary with paralleled success on the front of socialist construction The masses of poor and middle peasant have definitely taken the socialist path and no amount of effort of the class enemy will change their course In spite of all the pre dictions of the right wing oppor tunists that in one wav or anoth er we shall have to bow before the kulak and that the organi sation of state and collective farms will not succeed the Party registers victory after victory in the socialist reorganization of ag riculture The growing number of state and collective farms their economic consolidation speaks of the absolute victory of the general line of the Party and of the shattered hopes of our class ene mies that the socialist offensive will be broken Three years ago the Party un dertook the task of organizing large scale State grain farms Now even the blind can see that the line then adopted by the Party was correct Last spring the state farms sowed over 8 million hectares as compared with 3 mil lion the preceding year The"
  ],
